OL,3,CFlood defence ditches built on hill in
OL,4,C#76m scheme an 'eyesore'
OL,6,FFlood defences built in a #76 million
OL,7,Fscheme have been dubbed an "eyesore"
OL,8,Fby residents who claim they are being
OL,9,Fused to dump litter and have even
OL,10,Fdevalued their properties.
OL,12,FThe grassy ditches were dug by Severn
OL,13,FTrent Water in an area of Mansfield in
OL,14,Fnorth Nottinghamshire to shore up
OL,15,Fhomes against flooding.
OL,17,FBut residents say they are
OL,18,Funnecessary, claiming the area has not
OL,19,Fflooded in decades due to being on a
OL,20,Fhill.
