OL,3,CFlood defence ditches built on hill in
OL,4,C#76m scheme an 'eyesore'
OL,6,FRoger Brown, who has lived in the area
OL,7,Ffor 75 years, says a hole in the verge
OL,8,Foutside his home has instead
OL,9,Faccumulated litter and dog mess.
OL,11,F"It's an eyesore, a mess and it's
OL,12,Fdevalued my property by thousands," he
OL,13,Fsaid. "Who is going to buy this house
OL,14,Fnow with that outside? Nobody."
OL,16,FWhen ITV News visited Roger's home, a
OL,17,Fbeer bottle, food wrapper and plastic
OL,18,Fwaster were all sitting in the ditch
OL,19,Fvisible from his window.
OL,21,F'I hate them, I've always hated them'
