OL,3,CFlood defence ditches built on hill in
OL,4,C#76m scheme an 'eyesore'
OL,6,FThe installation is part of a #76
OL,7,Fmillion project that uses sustainable
OL,8,Fdrainage systems, known as SuDS, to
OL,9,Freduce the flood risk for houses in
OL,10,FMansfield.
OL,12,FA description on the company's website
OL,13,Fsays they work "by diverting surface
OL,14,Fwater away from sewers, slowing it
OL,15,Fdown and helping our drains to cope".
OL,17,FIt adds: "The great thing about SuDS
OL,18,Fis that they combine some of the
OL,19,Flatest water drainage technology with
OL,20,FMother Nature."
