OL,3,CFlood defence ditches built on hill in
OL,4,C#76m scheme an 'eyesore'
OL,6,FResident Jennie criticised the lack of
OL,7,Fupkeep of the defences, one of which
OL,8,Fsits outside her father's shop,
OL,9,Fclaiming they were also a safety
OL,10,Fhazard.
OL,12,F"I hate them, I've always hated them"
OL,13,Fshe said. "They look terrible,
OL,14,Fnobody's taken responsibility for
OL,15,Fmaintaining them."
