OL,3,CFlood defence ditches built on hill in
OL,4,C#76m scheme an 'eyesore'
OL,6,FJennie said a woman in a mobility
OL,7,Fscooter fell into one of them. "She
OL,8,Fcaught the corner with the edge of her
OL,9,Ftyre and the whole thing went in," she
OL,10,Fsaid. "It's abysmal, it's absolutely
OL,11,Fabysmal."
OL,13,FLocal Labour MP Steve Yemm said he'd
OL,14,Freceived a number of complaints from
OL,15,Fconstituents about the measures and
OL,16,Furged Severn Trent to act.
