OL,6,F"They've done this wrong", he said.
OL,7,F"They can either find some way of
OL,8,Fremediating it and putting it right,
OL,9,For they can compensate people who are
OL,10,Faffected appropriately".
OL,12,FA Severn Trent spokesperson told ITV
OL,13,FCalendar: "To increase the level of
OL,14,Fprotection from the devastation of
OL,15,Fsurface water flooding of homes and
OL,16,Fbusinesses, this three-year project
OL,17,Fhas been focussed on reducing the
OL,18,Fflood risk to people across in
OL,19,FMansfield.
