OL,6,F"Residents have been provided with
OL,7,Fregular updates ` with over 35,000
OL,8,Fletters, eleven drop-in events and
OL,9,Fface-to-face meetings on 80 different
OL,10,Fstreets.
OL,12,F"A virtual customer information centre
OL,13,Fis also featured on our website, which
OL,14,Fwas maintained and updated throughout
OL,15,Fthe project.
OL,17,F"In total, over 340 sustainable
OL,18,Fdrainage systems, adding 31 million
OL,19,Flitres of extra rainwater storage
OL,20,Fcapacity across the town will help
OL,21,Freduce the risk of flooding."
